You choose the suffering you want to experience. &ldquo;Suffer the pain of discipline or suffer the pain of regret.&rdquo;
As I struggle (and groan at the words that I&rsquo;m typing) to think and push through with this article, I know that at any time, I can just switch to a new tab and continue mindlessly browsing Twitter and Hacker News.
The problem with doing that is that I know that I&rsquo;ll hate myself in the morning when the feeling of having skipped a day clouds over me, and I&rsquo;d rather just kludge through writing this post even if I&rsquo;m really sleepy and tired.
